PRA Archive #: AZ1474

Description: Interview with Archbishop Oscar Arnulfo Romero and commentary all in Spanish. Contains interview with the outspoken critic of El Salvador's military government two days prior to his assassination. 

Romero condemns U.S. assistance to El Salvador, discusses security forces, the Christian democratic party, the worker-peasant coalition, and the church.

LAST INTERVIEW WITH ARCHBISHOP OSCAR ARNULFO ROMERO OF EL SALVADOR / produced by John Clements.
SERIES: El Salvador Now.